components.description:
**Destination-specific components**  override campaign-level components to send personalized content to each recipient.

Uses the same structure as [Meta's Components API](https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/message-templates/components) and [Postman reference](https://www.postman.com/meta/whatsapp-business-platform/folder/dybfz7u/components-object).

Supports:
- **header**: text / image / video / document
- **body**: named or positional parameters
- **button**: URL or coupon-code buttons

- **footer**: text

*Mutually exclusive* with `parameters`, `header_parameters`, and `buttons_parameters`.

**Example of destinations list with recipient-specific components:**
```json
{
  "destinations": [
    {
      "destination": "+11234567890",
      "components": [
        {
          "type": "body",
          "parameters": [
            { "type": "text", "parameter_name": "name", "text": "Alice" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "destination": "+10987654321",
      "components": [
        {
          "type": "body",
          "parameters": [
            { "type": "text", "parameter_name": "name", "text": "Bob" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

**Campaign-level components (global)**  applied to all recipients unless overridden by destination-specific components. Uses the same structure as [Meta's Components API](https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/message-templates/components) and [Postman reference](https://www.postman.com/meta/whatsapp-business-platform/folder/dybfz7u/components-object).

Supports:
- **header**: text / image / video / document
- **body**: named or positional parameters
- **button**: URL or coupon-code buttons

- **footer**: text

*Mutually exclusive* with `parameters` / `header_parameters` / `buttons_parameters`.

**Example highly_structured_message object with campaign-level components:**
```json
{
  "template": "template_company_campaign",
  "language_code": "en_US",
  "destinations": [
    { "destination": "+11234567890" },
    { "destination": "+10987654321" }
  ],
  "components": [
    {
      "type": "body",
      "parameters": [
        { "type": "text", "parameter_name": "company", "text": "Seasalt.ai" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
